importance of self-knowledge,

269
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:58,880
political awareness

270
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:04,656
and the necessity
for a deep and wide understanding

271
00:16:04,680 --> 00:16:07,136
of our commitments and our actions,

272
00:16:07,160 --> 00:16:08,480
how they affect others.

273
00:16:10,520 --> 00:16:11,976
So my plea today to everyone,

274
00:16:12,000 --> 00:16:16,480
especially those who sincerely
believe in Islamist jihadism ...

275
00:16:18,480 --> 00:16:20,880
refuse dogmatic authority;

276
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:26,040
let go of anger, hatred and violence;

277
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:28,776
learn to right wrongs

278
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:33,870
without even attempting to justify
cruel, unjust and futile behavior.

279
00:16:36,840 --> 00:16:40,176
Instead create a few
beautiful and useful things

280
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:41,400
that outlive us.

281
00:16:45,200 --> 00:16:47,056
Approach the world, life,

282
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:48,280
with love.

283
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,216
Learn to develop

284
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:52,496
or cultivate your hearts

285
00:16:52,520 --> 00:16:55,880
to see goodness, beauty and truth
in others and in the world.

286
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:59,520
That way we do matter
more to ourselves ...

287
00:17:01,240 --> 00:17:02,440
to each other,

288
00:17:03,160 --> 00:17:04,376
to our communities

289
00:17:04,400 --> 00:17:05,880
and, for me, to God.

290
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,616
This is jihad --

291
00:17:08,640 --> 00:17:09,840
my true jihad.

292
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:12,136
Thank you.

293
00:17:12,160 --> 00:17:14,600
(Applause)
